				"synopsis": {
					"type": 23,
					"value": "The player has given blood to the Infernal Vendor to make a unique potion. Once this potion is used, the player who gave the blood will feel sick after long rest (applying a debuff).\r\nThe potion's effect depends on the player, but the debuff is universal."
